Class LinuxDiskspaceJMXWrapper.DfData

java.lang.Object

Enclosing class:
LinuxDiskspaceJMXWrapper
public static class LinuxDiskspaceJMXWrapper.DfData
extends java.lang.Object

Class used as MXBean, representing a device/mount point and all its attendant data. Values are unitless and are used to represent either megabytes or inodes - the output of a df line.
